The paper deals with identifying the domain of a user query in an SMS-based search system. This involves natural language processing and classification of the query into a broad topic or domain. This falls under the sub-categories of Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Deep Learning (cs.DL), and Databases (cs.DB).
